metadata.name: Vitalik Inspired #1
metadata.description: On March 8 2023, Gitcoin released an NFT drop called 'Gitcoin Presents' with Vitalik Buterin, the founder of Ethereum, partnered to the project. Now a new collection is dropping, 'Vitalik Inspired' is a generative art with seed and parameters inferred from emotions of Vitalik over the years. Through iconic images, a generative algorithm has produced 1,000 art pieces.
